SUMMARY:🏒 Drop-In/Pickup – Sylvania\, OH
DESCRIPTION:D-League is&nbsp\;<strong>for newer players and those who aren't quite as skilled at the sport</strong>. To join a rec league at all\, you should already know the basics &mdash\; shooting\, skating\, stopping. However\, skills beyond these aren't guaranteed at this level. If you are new to hockey\, this will be the league you will start in.\nRink: Tam-O-Shanter Ice Rink – Sylvania\, OH\n~58 mi from Ann Arbor\nPrice: $10\nSource: DaySmart\nInfo: https://apps.daysmartrecreation.com/dash/x/#/online/tamoshanter/event-registration\nConfirm with rink — schedule subject to change.
